#. <section class="sutta" id="sn51.19"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.19:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.19:0.2"
msgid "2. Pāsādakampanavagga"
msgstr "2. Shaking the Stilt Longhouse"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 19. Iddhādidesanāsutta → bhāvanāsuttaṃ (bj) | desanā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn51.19:0.3"
msgid "19. Iddhādidesanāsutta"
msgstr "19. A Teaching on Psychic Power, Etc."

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.19:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Iddhiṃ vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi iddhipādañca iddhipādabhāvanañca "
"iddhipādabhāvanāgāminiñca paṭipadaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I will teach you psychic power, the bases of psychic power, the "
"development of the bases of psychic power, and the practice that leads to "
"the development of the bases of psychic power."

msgctxt "sn51.19:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.19:2.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, iddhi?"
msgstr "And what is psychic power?"

msgctxt "sn51.19:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhoti—ekopi hutvā "
"bahudhā hoti, bahudhāpi hutvā eko hoti … pe … yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ "
"vatteti—"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant wields the many kinds of psychic power: multiplying "
"themselves and becoming one again … controlling the body as far as the "
"Brahmā realm."

msgctxt "sn51.19:2.3"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, iddhi."
msgstr "This is called psychic power."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.19:3.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, iddhipādo?"
msgstr "And what is the basis of psychic power?"

msgctxt "sn51.19:3.2"
msgid ""
"Yo so, bhikkhave, maggo yā paṭipadā iddhilābhāya iddhipaṭilābhāya saṃvattati—"
msgstr "The path and practice that leads to gaining psychic power."

msgctxt "sn51.19:3.3"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, iddhipādo."
msgstr "This is called the basis of psychic power."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.19:4.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, iddhipādabhāvanā?"
msgstr "And what is the development of the bases of psychic power?"

msgctxt "sn51.19:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ "
"iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion "
"due to enthusiasm … "

msgctxt "sn51.19:4.3"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … pe …"
msgstr "energy …"

msgctxt "sn51.19:4.4"
msgid "cittasamādhi …"
msgstr "mental development …"

msgctxt "sn51.19:4.5"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti—"
msgstr "inquiry, and active effort."

msgctxt "sn51.19:4.6"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, iddhipādabhāvanā."
msgstr "This is called the development of the bases of psychic power."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.19:5.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, iddhipādabhāvanāgāminī paṭipadā?"
msgstr ""
"And what is the practice that leads to the development of the bases of "
"psychic power?"

msgctxt "sn51.19:5.2"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn51.19:5.3"
msgid ""
"sammādiṭṭhi, sammāsaṅkappo, sammāvācā, sammākammanto, sammāājīvo, "
"sammāvāyāmo, sammāsati, sammāsamādhi—"
msgstr ""
"right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn51.19:5.4"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, iddhipādabhāvanāgāminī paṭipadā”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is called the practice that leads to the development of the bases of "
"psychic power.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.19:5.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
